msgstr "Komunita"

#: mkdocs.yml:navigation get-help/index.md:meta.title get-help/index.md:title
#: get-help/index.md:block 1 (header) use-content/bot-traffic.md:block 15
#: (header)
msgid "Get help"
msgstr "Získajte pomoc"

#: index.md:meta.title index.md:title
msgid "Discover and build Wikimedia technology"
msgstr "Objavte a budujte technológiu Wikimedia"

#: index.md:block 1 (paragraph)
msgid "Find technical documentation, and connect with the developer community behind [Wikipedia](https://www.wikipedia.org/) and other [Wikimedia projects](https://wikimediafoundation.org/our-work/wikimedia-projects/)."
msgstr "Nájdite technickú dokumentáciu a spojte sa s komunitou vývojárov, ktorá stojí za [Wikipedia](https://www.wikipedia.org/) a ďalšími [wikimedia projektmi](https://wikimediafoundation.org/our-work/wikimedia-projects/) ."

#: index.md:block 2 (paragraph)
msgid "[Get started](get-started/){ .md-button }"
msgstr "[Začníte](začníte/){ .md-button }"

#: index.md:block 4 (header)
msgid "[Use Wikimedia content and data](use-content/)"
msgstr "[Použiť obsah a údaje Wikimedia] (použitie obsahu/)"

#: index.md:block 5 (paragraph) use-content/index.md:block 1 (paragraph)
msgid "Access articles from Wikipedia, media files, structured data, and more with public APIs and downloads."
msgstr "Získajte prístup k článkom z Wikipédie, mediálnym súborom, štruktúrovaným údajom a ďalším pomocou verejných rozhraní API a sťahovania."

#: index.md:block 7 (header)
msgid "[Build tools and bots](build-tools/)"
msgstr "[Vytvorte nástroje a boty] (budovať nástroje/)"

#: index.md:block 8 (paragraph) build-tools/index.md:block 1 (paragraph)
msgid "Tools and bots make it easier to edit and maintain Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Nástroje a roboty uľahčujú úpravu a údržbu projektov Wikimedia."

#: index.md:block 10 (header)
msgid "[Contribute to Wikimedia open source](contribute/)"
msgstr "[Prispejte do Wikimedia open source](prispejte/)"

#: index.md:block 11 (paragraph) contribute/index.md:block 1 (paragraph)
msgid "Help build the Wikimedia ecosystem with open source software."
msgstr "Pomôžte vybudovať ekosystém Wikimedia pomocou softvéru s otvoreným zdrojovým kódom."

#: index.md:block 13 (header)
msgid "[Connect with the community](community/)"
msgstr "[Spojte sa s komunitou](komunita/)"

#: index.md:block 14 (paragraph) community/index.md:block 1 (paragraph)
msgid "Get involved with the Wikimedia technical community, and find opportunities for support and learning."
msgstr "Zapojte sa do technickej komunity Wikimedia a nájdite príležitosti na podporu a učenie sa."

#: index.md:block 16 (header)
msgid "[Get help](get-help/)"
msgstr "[Získať pomoc](získať-pomoc/)"

#: index.md:block 17 (paragraph)
msgid "Find resources to help with questions and troubleshooting."
msgstr "Nájdi zdroje na pomoc pri otázkach a riešení problémov."

#: build-tools/index.md:block 2 (header)
msgid "[Discover and share tools](search.md)"
msgstr "[Objavte a zdieľajte nástroje](search.md)"

#: build-tools/index.md:block 3 (paragraph) build-tools/search.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Browse the catalog of tools on Toolhub, share your tools, and help maintain tool metadata."
msgstr "Prehliadajte si katalóg nástrojov na Toolhub, zdieľajte svoje nástroje a pomôžte udržiavať metadáta nástrojov."

#: build-tools/index.md:block 4 (header)
msgid "[Get started](get-started.md)"
msgstr "[Začať] [Začať.md]"

#: build-tools/index.md:block 5 (paragraph) build-tools/get-started.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Create your first tool, learn about running a bot, and get best practices."
msgstr "Vytvorte si svoj prvý nástroj, naučte sa spúšťať robota a získajte osvedčené postupy."

#: build-tools/index.md:block 6 (header) get-started/index.md:block 5 (header)
#: use-content/index.md:block 4 (header)
msgid "[Learn with tutorials](tutorials.md)"
msgstr "[Učte sa pomocou návodov](tutorials.md)"

#: build-tools/index.md:block 7 (paragraph) build-tools/tutorials.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Follow step-by-step guides to learn the basics of interacting with Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Postupujte podľa podrobných sprievodcov, aby ste sa naučili základy interakcie s projektmi Wikimedia."

#: build-tools/index.md:block 8 (header)
msgid "[Use APIs and data sources](apis.md)"
msgstr "[Využívajte API a zdroje údajov] (apis.md)"

#: build-tools/index.md:block 9 (paragraph) build-tools/apis.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Explore programming interfaces for building bots and tools."
msgstr "Prejdite do programovacích rozhraní na budovanie robotov a nástrojov."

#: build-tools/index.md:block 10 (header)
msgid "[Host tools on Wikimedia servers](host-tools.md)"
msgstr "[Nástroje hostiteľa na serveroch Wikimedia](host-tools.md)"

#: build-tools/index.md:block 11 (paragraph) build-tools/host-tools.md:block 2
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Access cloud services for performing analytics, administering bots, running web services, and hosting tools that help Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Získajte prístup k cloudovým službám na vykonávanie analýz, správu robotov, spúšťanie webových služieb a hostingové nástroje, ktoré pomáhajú projektom Wikimedia."

#: build-tools/apis.md:meta.title build-tools/apis.md:title
#: build-tools/apis.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Use APIs and data sources"
msgstr "Používajte rozhrania API a zdroje údajov"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 3 (header) contribute/by-language.md:block 3
#: (header)
#, optional
msgid "Pywikibot"
msgstr "Pywikibot"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 4 (paragraph) contribute/by-language.md:block 4
#: (paragraph)
msgid "Pywikibot is a Python library and collection of scripts that automate work on Wikimedia projects."
msgstr "Pywikibot je knižnica Python a zbierka skriptov, ktoré automatizujú prácu na projektoch Wikimedia."

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 5 (unordered list)
#: contribute/by-language.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot)"
msgstr "[Prečítajte si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 5 (unordered list)
#: contribute/by-language.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Contribute](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot/Development)"
msgstr "[Prispieť](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot/Development)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 5 (unordered list)
#: contribute/by-language.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Get the source code](https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/g/pywikibot/core)"
msgstr "[Získať zdrojový kód](https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/g/pywikibot/core)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 6 (header) use-content/content.md:block 9
#: (header)
msgid "Browse libraries by programming language"
msgstr "Prehliadajte knižnice podľa programovacieho jazyka"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 7 (paragraph)
#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 2 (paragraph)
#: use-content/content.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "API client libraries make it easier to write code that interacts with an API. Visit this list to browse popular libraries for the MediaWiki API by programming language."
msgstr "Klientske knižnice API uľahčujú písanie kódu, ktorý komunikuje s API. V tomto zozname si môžete prehliadať obľúbené knižnice pre MediaWiki API podľa programovacieho jazyka."

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 8 (unordered list)
#: get-started/browse-languages.md:block 3 (unordered list)
#: use-content/content.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Client_code)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Client_code)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 9 (header) use-content/content.md:block 12
#: (header)
msgid "Use the API"
msgstr "Použite API"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 10 (paragraph) use-content/content.md:block 13
#: (paragraph)
msgid "The MediaWiki API gives you programmatic access to content on any Wikimedia wiki. You can use the API to search and display wiki pages, get media files, edit pages, and manage wikis."
msgstr "MediaWiki API vám poskytuje programový prístup k obsahu na ľubovoľnej wiki Wikimedia. Pomocou API môžete vyhľadávať a zobrazovať wiki stránky, získavať mediálne súbory, upravovať stránky a spravovať wiki."

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 11 (unordered list) use-content/content.md:block
#: 14 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Action_API)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Action_API)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 11 (unordered list) use-content/content.md:block
#: 14 (unordered list)
msgid "[Try the sandbox](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:ApiSandbox)"
msgstr "[Vyskúšať pieskovisko](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:ApiSandbox)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 12 (header) use-content/content.md:block 15
#: (header) use-content/data.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Download content in bulk"
msgstr "Stiahnite obsah hromadne"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 13 (paragraph) use-content/content.md:block 16
#: (paragraph) use-content/data.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "Access free downloads of wiki content and data that you can use in research, offline reading, bot editing, and other projects."
msgstr "Získajte bezplatné súbory na stiahnutie s obsahom a dátami wiki, ktoré môžete použiť pri výskume, čítaní offline, úpravách botmi a v ďalších projektoch."

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 14 (unordered list) use-content/content.md:block
#: 17 (unordered list) use-content/data.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Data_dumps)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Data_dumps)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 15 (header)
msgid "Query wiki databases"
msgstr "Dotazujte sa na wiki databázy"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 16 (paragraph)
msgid "Wiki replicas are anonymized versions of the databases that back Wikimedia's production sites. Use Quarry to run and share SQL queries."
msgstr "Wiki repliky sú anonymizované verzie databáz, na ktorých bežia produkčné stránky Wikimedia. Pomocou nástroja Quarry môžete spúšťať a zdieľať SQL dotazy."

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit Quarry](https://quarry.wmcloud.org/)"
msgstr "[Navštíviť Quarry](https://quarry.wmcloud.org/)"

#: build-tools/apis.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Research:Quarry)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Meta-Wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Research:Quarry)"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 3 (header) build-tools/tutorials.md:block
#: 3 (header)
msgid "Build your first tool"
msgstr "Vytvorte svoj prvý nástroj"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 4 (paragraph)
#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to edit wiki pages using Python and the Pywikibot framework. This tutorial helps you get started quickly using only your browser."
msgstr "Naučte sa upravovať wiki stránky pomocou jazyka Python a frameworku Pywikibot. Tento návod vám pomôže rýchlo začať len s použitím prehliadača."

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 5 (unordered list)
#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot/PAWS)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Pywikibot/PAWS)"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Learn about creating and running bots"
msgstr "Spoznajte vytváranie a spúšťanie botov"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Bots help maintain wikis by performing repetitive tasks. Get started creating and running bots by learning about best practices."
msgstr "Boty pomáhajú udržiavať wiki vykonávaním opakujúcich sa úloh. Začnite vytvárať a spúšťať boty oboznámením sa s osvedčenými postupmi."

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Creating_a_bot)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Creating_a_bot)"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Best practices for open source tools"
msgstr "Osvedčené postupy pre open source nástroje"

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "New to open source? Get tips to help you develop successful tools and bots, including choosing a license, publishing the code, and writing docs."
msgstr "Ste v open source nováčik? Získajte tipy, ktoré vám pomôžu vyvíjať úspešné nástroje a boty, vrátane výberu licencie, zverejnenia kódu a písania dokumentácie."

#: build-tools/get-started.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Toolforge/Developing_successful_tools)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Toolforge/Developing_successful_tools)"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:meta.title build-tools/host-tools.md:title
#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Host tools on Wikimedia servers"
msgstr "Hostujte nástroje na serveroch Wikimedia"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 3 (header)
msgid "Run scripts in your browser"
msgstr "Spúšťajte skripty vo svojom prehliadači"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "PAWS is a free, cloud-hosted playground for creating scripts and data visualizations related to Wikimedia projects. Log in with your Wikimedia account and create a notebook to get started."
msgstr "PAWS je bezplatné cloudové ihrisko na vytváranie skriptov a vizualizácií dát súvisiacich s projektmi Wikimedia. Prihláste sa svojím účtom Wikimedia a začnite vytvorením poznámkového bloku (notebook)."

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit PAWS](https://hub-paws.wmcloud.org/)"
msgstr "[Navštíviť PAWS](https://hub-paws.wmcloud.org/)"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/PAWS)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/PAWS)"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Learn about cloud hosting for tools"
msgstr "Spoznajte cloudový hosting pre nástroje"

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Toolforge is a free hosting environment for running and managing tools. Developing a tool in Toolforge makes it easier to access Wikimedia content and data and to share your tool with others."
msgstr "Toolforge je bezplatné hostingové prostredie na spúšťanie a správu nástrojov. Vývoj nástroja v Toolforge uľahčuje prístup k obsahu a dátam Wikimedia a zdieľanie vášho nástroja s ostatnými."

#: build-tools/host-tools.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Toolforge)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Wikitech](https://wikitech.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Toolforge)"

#: build-tools/search.md:meta.title build-tools/search.md:title
#: build-tools/search.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Discover and share tools"
msgstr "Objavujte a zdieľajte nástroje"

#: build-tools/search.md:block 3 (header) use-content/featured-apps.md:block
#: 12 (header)
#, optional
msgid "Toolhub"
msgstr "Toolhub"

#: build-tools/search.md:block 4 (paragraph) contribute/search.md:block 13
#: (paragraph) use-content/featured-apps.md:block 13 (paragraph)
msgid "Toolhub is a catalog of tools that make it easier to edit and maintain Wikimedia projects. Use Toolhub to discover new tools, connect with tool maintainers, and share lists of your favorite tools."
msgstr "Toolhub je katalóg nástrojov, ktoré uľahčujú úpravu a údržbu projektov Wikimedia. Pomocou Toolhubu objavujte nové nástroje, spojte sa so správcami nástrojov a zdieľajte zoznamy svojich obľúbených nástrojov."

#: build-tools/search.md:block 5 (unordered list) contribute/search.md:block
#: 14 (unordered list) use-content/featured-apps.md:block 14 (unordered list)
msgid "[Visit Toolhub](https://toolhub.wikimedia.org/)"
msgstr "[Navštíviť Toolhub](https://toolhub.wikimedia.org/)"

#: build-tools/search.md:block 6 (header)
msgid "Share a tool"
msgstr "Zdieľajte nástroj"

#: build-tools/search.md:block 7 (paragraph)
msgid "Add your tool to the Toolhub catalog so others can benefit from and build on your work. Log in to Toolhub with your Wikimedia account to get started."
msgstr "Pridajte svoj nástroj do katalógu Toolhub, aby z vašej práce mohli ťažiť aj ostatní a stavať na nej. Začnite prihlásením do Toolhubu svojím účtom Wikimedia."

#: build-tools/search.md:block 8 (unordered list)
msgid "[Add a tool to Toolhub](https://toolhub.wikimedia.org/add-or-remove-tools?tab=tool-create)"
msgstr "[Pridať nástroj do Toolhubu](https://toolhub.wikimedia.org/add-or-remove-tools?tab=tool-create)"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:meta.title build-tools/tutorials.md:title
#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 1 (header)
#: get-started/tutorials.md:meta.title get-started/tutorials.md:title
#: use-content/tutorials.md:meta.title use-content/tutorials.md:title
#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 1 (header)
msgid "Learn with tutorials"
msgstr "Učte sa pomocou návodov"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 6 (header) use-content/tutorials.md:block 12
#: (header)
msgid "Generate ideas for articles"
msgstr "Generujte nápady na články"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 7 (paragraph) use-content/tutorials.md:block
#: 13 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to use the MediaWiki API to generate ideas for new Wikipedia articles. This tutorial uses Python and the Flask framework."
msgstr "Naučte sa používať MediaWiki API na generovanie nápadov na nové články Wikipédie. Tento návod používa Python a framework Flask."

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 8 (unordered list)
#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 14 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Article_ideas_generator)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Article_ideas_generator)"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 9 (header)
msgid "Write a bot that uses Wikidata"
msgstr "Napíšte bota, ktorý používa Wikidáta"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 10 (paragraph)
msgid "Use Python to handle large datasets from Wikidata and transfer data between tools in your workflow."
msgstr "Pomocou jazyka Python spracujte veľké súbory dát z Wikidát a prenášajte dáta medzi nástrojmi vo svojom pracovnom postupe."

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 11 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on Wikidata](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Pywikibot_-_Python_3_Tutorial)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac na Wikidátach](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Wikidata:Pywikibot_-_Python_3_Tutorial)"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 12 (header) use-content/tutorials.md:block 3
#: (header)
msgid "Display holidays from Wikipedia"
msgstr "Zobrazte sviatky z Wikipédie"

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 13 (paragraph)
#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 4 (paragraph)
msgid "Learn how to use the MediaWiki API to fetch holidays for a given date from Wikipedia. This tutorial also covers how to use the API to log in to Wikipedia and add new holidays. This tutorial uses Python and the Flask framework."
msgstr "Naučte sa používať MediaWiki API na získavanie sviatkov pre daný dátum z Wikipédie. Tento návod sa venuje aj tomu, ako pomocou API prihlásiť sa do Wikipédie a pridávať nové sviatky. Návod používa Python a framework Flask."

#: build-tools/tutorials.md:block 14 (unordered list)
#: use-content/tutorials.md:block 5 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more on mediawiki.org](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/API:Holidays_viewer)"
