#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 15 (header)
msgid "Learn how to submit code"
msgstr "Zistite, ako odoslať kód"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 16 (paragraph)
msgid "Wikimedia uses Gerrit and GitLab for code review. Before you submit code, get familiar with the tools, processes, and best practices."
msgstr "Wikimedia používa na revíziu kódu Gerrit a GitLab. Skôr než odošlete kód, oboznámte sa s nástrojmi, procesmi a osvedčenými postupmi."

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more about Gerrit](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Gerrit/Tutorial)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac o Gerrite](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Gerrit/Tutorial)"

#: get-started/new-dev.md:block 17 (unordered list)
msgid "[Read more about GitLab](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/GitLab)"
msgstr "[Prečítať si viac o GitLabe](https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/GitLab)"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 2 (header)
msgid "Tutorials for using content and data"
msgstr "Návody na používanie obsahu a dát"

#: get-started/tutorials.md:block 3 (paragraph)
